Function: isperfectpower
Section: number_theoretical
C-Name: isperfectpower
Prototype: lGD&
Help: isperfectpower(x,{&n}): return the maximal k >= 1 such that x = n^k is a
 perfect power. If n is given puts the exact k-th root there.
Description: 
 (int):small       isperfectpower($1, NULL)
 (int, &int):small isperfectpower($1, &$2)

